Projects

Movie Finder

Live Demo | GitHub

A web application that allows users to search for movies and view details about them. Users can also create an account and save movies to their favorites list.

Built with React, Redux, TypeScript, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, Sass, Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and the OMDb API.

Weather App

Live Demo | GitHub

A web application that allows users to search for the weather in any city in the world.

Built with React, TypeScript, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, Sass, and the OpenWeatherMap API.

Todo App

Live Demo | GitHub

A web application that allows users to create a todo list.

Built with React, TypeScript, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, Sass, and Redux.
